  "body": "I want to be able to 1) expose a Deployment as a service and 2) attach to a running Deployment.\n\nSo a couple of enhancements that may need to happen in kubectl:\n\n``` sh\n# Generates a service that exposes the nginx deployment\n$ kubectl expose deployment/nginx\n# Runs a new image under a Deployment and attaches to the oldest pod\n$ kubectl run nginx --image=nginx --generator=deployment/v1beta1 --attach\n```\n\n@kubernetes/kubectl @nikhiljindal \n",
